{"TopicId":196797,"ForumId":70,"TopicTitle":"KSP switches to desktop resolution on scene change","CreatedByName":"DocRockwell","CreatedById":174979,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-09-09T00:25:12Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"DocRockwell","CreatedById":174979,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-09-09T00:25:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nChanging scenes (ie \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E to \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E) and sometimes alt-tabbing causes KSP to revert from whatever resolution I set it to, to the desktop resolution. How do I prevent this incredibly annoying behavior?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"jimmymcgoochie","CreatedById":199902,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-09-09T11:42:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSet your desktop resolution to be the same as KSP (or vice versa), or download and use the AnyRes mod which lets you change the screen resolution anywhere in the game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022129964\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed3277367070\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/170160-190-anyres-continued-change-your-screen-resolution-on-the-fly/\u0026amp;tab=comments\u0026amp;do=embed\u0026amp;comment=3279234\u0026amp;embedComment=3279234\u0026amp;embedDo=findComment#comment-3279234\u0022 style=\u0022height:295px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}